    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="writingSession">
                <opener>
                    <dateline><pb/> Essex S<hi rendition="#sup">t</hi><lb/>Manches.</dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Engels,</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>To day is preeminently one for a walk. What do you say
                    to starting at 4 &amp; dining with me at 6.</p>
                <closer>Your <expan>faith<ex>fully</ex></expan><lb/>Isaac Hall </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
